First is my dear bro Cyrikwardzurr (a tanky cleric if I've ever seen one) and his group idea... which is so crazy it just might work.  Clerics are more versatile than most people give us credit for, and with the right gear we can take on some alternate roles.  Cyrik's idea is that a great group could be made up of 6 clerics... 2 to tank, 2 to heal, 2 to stun/root... and we could rotate roles as mana permits.  It definitely has its appeal ---- has anyone tried this?  Thoughts? (and oo charm of the brotherhood - could be nice)<br>
<br>
