We have dots that are undead only but far worse ratios than any other classes general dots even though they are specialised.<br>
<br>
The made is so we can use affliction 4 items thinking this is good, but from point 1, the cost of the item and the fact that they like to make all high level undead summon or unrootable means we cant use the dots anyway...<br>
<br>
Best way ive found to solo is get your ds up as much as you can (shammy potion is best and not overly expensive) pull with reverse ds to add even more, throw in your hammer pet and melee melee melee and heal as needed.<br>
<br>
at 62 i can still fight dark blues this way (with other add ons like kei and beneficial awareness 4 potion - 5% mana press on heals, at 61 i could do 3 db mobs back to back before oom with good gear)<br>
<br>
aas also make it easier as you get more, better healing, better mana ratio, less damage taken...<br>
<br>
62 is harder to solo at than 61 though, if you like to solo occasionally id reccomend staying at 61 and getting some aas before going higher (or stay at the 61/62 border so can solo at 61 and group at 62 as appropriate)<br>
